'''阿什兰'''（{{lang-en|Ashland}}）位于[[美国|美国]][[亚拉巴马州|亚拉巴马州]]东部，是[[克莱县_(亚拉巴马州)|克莱县]]的县治所在{{GR|6}}，面积18.8平方公里。根据[[美国2000年人口普查|2000年人口普查]]，共有1,965人，其中[[白人|白人]]占73.74%、[[非裔美国人|非裔美国人]]占25.29%。{{GR|2}}根据2050年人口估計，本鎮共有1,885人。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Population Estiames- Alabama |publisher=United States Census Bureau |url=http://www.census.gov/popest/cities/files/SUB-EST2005-all.csv |format=CSV |accessdate=January 20, 2010 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100210200305/http://www.census.gov/popest/cities/files/SUB-EST2005-all.csv |archivedate=2010-02-10 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

==地理==
阿什兰的座標為{{Coord|33|16|20|N|85|50|13|W|type:city}}（33.272206,-85.836925）。{{GR|1}}根據[[美國2000年人口普查|2000年人口普查]]，本城面積為{{convert|7.3|sqmi|sqkm|2}}，其中{{convert|7.2|sqmi|sqkm|2}}為陸地，{{convert|0.04|sqmi|sqkm|2}}為水域。<ref name ="Gazetteer files">{{cite web|title=US Gazetteer files 2010|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|publisher=[[United_States_Census_Bureau|United States Census Bureau]]|accessdate=2013-01-25|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/699nOulzi?url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|archive-date=2012-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=2000censusarea>{{Cite web | title = Geographic Comparison Table | work = American Fast Facts | publisher = United States Census Bureau | url = http://factfinder.census.gov/servlet/GCTTable?_bm=y&-geo_id=04000US01&-_box_head_nbr=GCT-PH1&-ds_name=DEC_2000_SF1_U&-redoLog=false&-mt_name=DEC_2000_SF1_U_GCTPH1_US9&-format=ST-7 accessdate =13 January 2010 | access-date = 2013-08-12 | archive-url = https://archive.today/20200212033847/http://factfinder.census.gov/servlet/GCTTable?_bm=y&-geo_id=04000US01&-_box_head_nbr=GCT-PH1&-ds_name=DEC_2000_SF1_U&-redoLog=false&-mt_name=DEC_2000_SF1_U_GCTPH1_US9&-format=ST-7 | archive-date = 2020-02-12 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>阿什兰海拔為{{convert|1130|ft|m}}，是亚拉巴马州海拔最高城市。{{GR|3}}

